### SIMPLE JWT TEST - Từng bước một

### Bước 1: Test AuthService trực tiếp
POST http://localhost:5060/api/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

###

### Bước 2: Test qua API Gateway
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

###

### Bước 3: Test không có token (phải lỗi 401)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing

###

### Bước 4: Test có token (thay YOUR_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###